title.en: Decision of Conservation and Restoration Intervention Ontology Special Instances

description.en:
DCRIO Special Instances specialises Decision of Conservation and Restoration Intervention Ontology with classes, properties and individuals about specific categories of interventions options. At this version the model contains special classes, properties and individuals related to intervention options of i) cleaning superficial deposits and ii) consolidation of flaking of gouache artworks.

The ontology directly imports Decision of Conservation and Restoration Intervention Ontology and DCRIO Vocabulary.

The ontology indirectly imports SKOS, CIDOC CRM, CRMsci and selected object properties from the CIDOC CRM extension about typed properties and negative typed properties.
